Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper deals with the detection and classification of skin cancer using image processing and deep learning techniques, which falls under the domain of computer vision. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses Convolutional Neural Network (CNN) and Transfer Learning methods for the classification of skin cancer, which falls under the domain of machine learning. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses AI-based techniques for the detection and classification of skin cancer. 
4. cs.IR (Information Retrieval): The paper deals with the retrieval of information from dermoscopy images of skin cancer for the purpose of diagnosis. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with the analysis of multimedia data (dermoscopy images) for the detection and classification of skin cancer.
